# Max Uint16

> Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

<section class="usage">

## Usage

```javascript
var UINT16_MAX = require( '@stdlib/constants/math/uint16-max' );
```

#### UINT16_MAX

Maximum unsigned 16-bit integer.

```javascript
var bool = ( UINT16_MAX === 65535 );
// returns true
```

</section>
